constructNewFormChoice

protected FormChoice constructNewFormChoice(java.awt.Dimension formChoiceSize)
constructNewFormChoice method creates a new FormChoice component with the specified sizes. Note that this technique is necessary to work with component sizing in the AWT. In the AWT, certain layout managers mixed with particular panels causes the components setSize method to get ignored, even though the layout manager's layout policies may state otherwise. AWT certainly is not as robust as the SWING architecture. Another form of proof that windows sucks!!!
Parameters:
formChoiceSize:Ljava.awt.Dimension - the preferred, minimum and maximum size of the form component.
Returns:
a Ljjb.toolbox.form.FormChoice component.
